{"tid":495839,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【內有惡喵】英夫婦養貓養到要買「三保」　到底咩貓咁大陣仗？","createTime":"2017-12-11T06:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T09:55:51.000Z","uid":10958,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b130f257c4a98929543e8373fd6ce0ae24b3149a","tid":495839,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>【內有惡喵】英夫婦養貓養到要買「三保」　到底咩貓咁大陣仗？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/139856/thumbnail/f585e1689bf33e333ac8ea2c282e5b58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F139856%2Fthumbnail%2Ff585e1689bf33e333ac8ea2c282e5b58.jpg&h=8de5d087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國人喜愛動物，養貓也很普遍。然而，英國有對夫婦養的貓，竟然需要購買「三保」，當中所為何事？<br />\n居住在英國奧爾德姆鎮（Oldham）的Jones夫婦為了家中貓咪，不得不購買俗稱「三保」的第三責任保險，以保障附近居民。驟耳聽來很荒謬，但實際上是如沒有購買「三保」的話，Jones夫婦是不能繼續飼養那貓的。到底他們所養的，是一隻怎麼樣的貓？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040853/xlarge/acd58850360a52c97050ff986c33155f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040853%2Fxlarge%2Facd58850360a52c97050ff986c33155f.jpg&h=7d7ac9bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Jones夫婦飼養的藪貓Anubis，11周大已長達一米。（kinganubis17@Instagram）</span><br />\n<br />\n藪貓多棲息於非洲大草原，是一種雜食性的動物，主要食糧為野兔、昆蟲、雀鳥等等，屬於稀少的動物。雖然不少人對於Jones夫婦所領養的這隻藪貓感到好奇，但同時也擔心牠會野性突發，傷及附近居民，尤其是老人家和小孩子。為了得到當地政府許可，Jones夫婦需要購買公共責任保險，才能將藪貓帶至公共場合，但至於保費、保額，以及保障內容，他們則未有公布。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040864/xlarge/f285790f484048a0fc4e2c068856ba67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040864%2Fxlarge%2Ff285790f484048a0fc4e2c068856ba67.jpg&h=3a236df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040867/xlarge/2d2a7473b7b5da0b903bcfc8fdafb24a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040867%2Fxlarge%2F2d2a7473b7b5da0b903bcfc8fdafb24a.jpg&h=72638e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040870/xlarge/d5a4fe24d326f775b5bb7ef36ae9d4c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040870%2Fxlarge%2Fd5a4fe24d326f775b5bb7ef36ae9d4c0.jpg&h=f65f88fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040865/xlarge/453a2b09cda7eab92b76b0d2bd6e95dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040865%2Fxlarge%2F453a2b09cda7eab92b76b0d2bd6e95dd.jpg&h=6926c7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040866/xlarge/6758157796f81c346f85077957a7d54a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040866%2Fxlarge%2F6758157796f81c346f85077957a7d54a.jpg&h=dc6bbc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040872/xlarge/cabfba7c04da5463cf357734350f1720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040872%2Fxlarge%2Fcabfba7c04da5463cf357734350f1720.jpg&h=b785b7c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040869/xlarge/13b8d151648f48df15685ef012b7a7d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040869%2Fxlarge%2F13b8d151648f48df15685ef012b7a7d1.jpg&h=8649f213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040868/xlarge/c9ac52ed32a7366cab0cc384c0f5737e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040868%2Fxlarge%2Fc9ac52ed32a7366cab0cc384c0f5737e.jpg&h=718c6aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這隻藪貓名叫Anubis，雖然只有11周大，但身長已達1米多，估計一年後Anubis的體型會比現時還要大一倍。Jones夫婦也知道飼養藪貓有一定的潛在風險，為了兩個可愛的孩子，4歲的Sienna和10歲Brandon，Jones太太已做好一切保護措施。她表示：「雖然孩子會與Anubis一起睡，但決不會讓他們單獨相處。我們還特別在家外建了防護欄及攝影機，確保Anubis的任何舉動都不會構成意外。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040954/xlarge/8fa77c0c68e3a356ca4fedf763d772ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040954%2Fxlarge%2F8fa77c0c68e3a356ca4fedf763d772ce.jpg&h=658a1791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">藪貓在捕獵時的行動以垂直奔跳爲主。（kinganubis17@Instagram）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\nAnubis有牠專屬的Instagram帳戶，還有近萬名粉絲追隨。Jones太太表示，當地居民乎都很喜歡Anubis，每天都會收到世界各地不同查詢，而最常見的，就是問及有關飼養藪貓的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040873/xlarge/23fd86ac56f5b761d5ac383adf937814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040873%2Fxlarge%2F23fd86ac56f5b761d5ac383adf937814.jpg&h=03639050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040871/xlarge/64afcf8b704e1342d6cc0826cee4c71b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040871%2Fxlarge%2F64afcf8b704e1342d6cc0826cee4c71b.jpg&h=af885720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040874/xlarge/4535f0d94b1d0511617ce53209e71476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040874%2Fxlarge%2F4535f0d94b1d0511617ce53209e71476.jpg&h=f7f729d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，Jones夫婦都會勸籲有意飼養者三思，因為藪貓不好養，所花的費用也很高昂。據悉，一頭藪貓在當索價高達1.2萬英鎊（約12萬港元），其實動物收容所有那麼多待領動物，想養貓也不必購買這類較難飼養而有危險性的品種？改為領養家貓會更理想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/139856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F139856&d=K3Mti2WBIh1zTkKWbeZO7KNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=7e141ed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/139856</a>"},{"pid":"5771c5d43590d459e905ffb545a2b7aa6e26a8ba","tid":495839,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"